derivedAttributes.attrExprVal:
DI_CF(CASE WHEN  SRC_SUPPLIER.EMAIL LIKE '%_@_%__%'
THEN
 SRC_SUPPLIER.EMAIL
ELSE
'Invalid email address'
END)

mJnr_Inst_Cnds.jnrCnd: SRC_SUPPLIER.ADDRESS_LINE_1=SRC_D_ADDRESS.Address_line_1 ANDSRC_SUPPLIER.ADDRESS_LINE_2=SRC_D_ADDRESS.Address_line_2 ANDSRC_SUPPLIER.CITY=SRC_D_ADDRESS.City ANDSRC_SUPPLIER.State=SRC_D_ADDRESS.state ANDSRC_SUPPLIER.COUNTRY=SRC_D_ADDRESS.Country ANDSRC_SUPPLIER.ZIPCODE=SRC_D_ADDRESS.Zipcode

attributes.attrExprVal:
DI_CF(CASE WHEN(SRC_D_SUPPLIER_1.Supplier_id IS NULL) THEN 1
WHEN (SRC_D_SUPPLIER_1.Supplier_id IS NOT NULL AND
(SRC_D_SUPPLIER_1.Address_key<>SRC_D_ADDRESS.Address_key OR
SRC_D_SUPPLIER_1.Email<>SRC_SUPPLIER.EMAIL OR 
SRC_D_SUPPLIER_1.Phone<>SRC_SUPPLIER.PHONE OR
SRC_D_SUPPLIER_1.Supplier_desc<>SRC_SUPPLIER.SUPPLIER_DESC))
THEN 2
ELSE 0
END)
